algorithm:
The new algorithm involves scoring each bin based on the ratio of the remaining capacity of the bin to the logarithm of the reciprocal of the item size, and subtracting it from the maximum capacity of the bins.

Code:
code:
import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    scores = (bins / np.log(1/item)) - max_capacity
    return scores
